HEADWORD: Immovability
<hw>Im*mov"a*bil"i*ty</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>The quality
or state of being immovable; fixedness; steadfastness; <as>as,
<ex>immovability</ex> of a heavy body; <ex>immovability</ex> of
purpose.</as></def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

